          <actionDate>2019-02-27</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Smaller Class Sizes for Students and Educators Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Education to award grants for local educational agencies in high-poverty school districts&nbsp;to reduce class sizes in the early elementary grades (kindergarten through third grade) by recruiting, training, and hiring qualified teachers.</p> <ul> <ul> </ul></ul>]]></text>
